<sec id="code-availability">
  <title>Code Availability</title>
  <p>The source code for <monospace>FAIRLinked</monospace> can be
  retrieved
  <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://pypi.org/project/FAIRLinked/">from
  PyPi</ext-link> or in the
  <ext-link ext-link-type="uri" xlink:href="https://github.com/cwru-sdle/FAIRLinked">GitHub
  repository</ext-link>.</p>
</sec>
